murder-suicide, they can go.

34:57.354 --> 35:00.744
Anybody asks about the overtime,
put it on Lomax's Gold Card.

35:11.194 --> 35:13.708
- Straps are just makin' him worse.
- They're for his own safety.

35:13.794 --> 35:16.592
- Unstrap him.
- They're for his own safety.

35:16.634 --> 35:19.023
All right. Simon,
