35:19.114 --> 35:22.823
Take it easy. Simon, just calm down.
All right?

35:22.914 --> 35:26.429
Mommy! Daddy!
Mommy! Daddy!

35:26.514 --> 35:29.472
Tell him to turn that off!

35:29.554 --> 35:31.784
Turn the siren off!

35:31.834 --> 35:33.711
Simon, ho. Hey!

35:33.754 --> 35:37.713
Now look. Who's this? ls that your
