35:48.194 --> 35:51.072
''Do not touch. lt may be hot.''
That's very good advice.

35:51.154 --> 35:54.863
ls that your teacher?
Dr. London?

35:54.954 --> 35:58.663
She's your friend, right?
My name is Art. l'm your friend too.

35:58.754 --> 36:01.666
Art is a stranger!

36:01.714 --> 36:04.751
Art is a stranger!

36:06.914 --> 36:09.553
Art is a stranger!

36:09.594 --> 36:11.471
Okay, strap him in.

36:11.514 --> 36:14.665
l won't hurt you.

36:26.874 --> 36:30.184
- Hi. Are you the doctor?
