just give him a shot?

36:35.674 --> 36:37.983
He's autistic.

36:38.034 --> 36:40.594
- Autistic?
- Uh-huh.

36:40.674 --> 36:43.472
What does that mean?

36:43.554 --> 36:45.465
Nothing gets through?

36:45.554 --> 36:48.990
No, it's just the opposite.
Everything gets through.

36:49.074 --> 36:51.793
He has trouble with feelings
and emotions.

36:51.834 --> 36:54.826
So he gets very frightened
and confused.

36:54.874 --> 36:59.629
Wait. l'm not gonna be able
to question this boy?

36:59.674 --> 37:01.392
Probably not.

37:01.474 --> 37:03.430
Sorry.

37:17.554 --> 37:19.385
Take care of him.

37:25.554 --> 37:27.829
Why are we doing this, Dean?

37:27.914 --> 37:30.747
Why does he want to see us?
We didn't do anything wrong, right?

37:30.834 --> 37:32.586
Should l turn around?

37:32.674 --> 37:35.552
- No, he'd kill us.
- He might kill us anyway.

37:35.634 --> 37:39.388
- Are you being serious?
- Relax, Leo, please.

37:52.834 --> 37:55.302
Okay, l'm scared.
l'm gettin' really, really scared.

37:55.394 --> 37:59.387
Leo, stop it. We're doing this together.
We didn't break any laws.

37:59.474 --> 38:03.706
