by this code.

39:48.034 --> 39:50.025
We can save their lives.

39:50.114 --> 39:54.232
l give you my pledge.
l want you to give me yours.

39:54.314 --> 39:57.704
Diligence, loyalty
and above all...

39:59.514 --> 40:01.391
absolute silence.

40:03.714 --> 40:06.512
This is kind of an interesting story.

40:06.554 --> 40:09.068
The television program 60 Minutes
right here on CBS?

