Where is everyone?

41:47.914 --> 41:49.950
Where's the police? Where's the guard
that was sitting right here?

41:50.034 --> 41:52.070
They were called off half an hour ago.
Told they weren't needed.

41:52.114 --> 41:54.389
Take me to see Simon Lynch right now.
Unlock that door.

41:54.474 --> 41:57.307
We just transferred him
