42:03.034 --> 42:05.912
l could understand.
They didn't want their little kid on--

42:43.314 --> 42:45.270
Can l help you?

42:47.154 --> 42:49.714
Hi. l'm with the F.B.l.

42:49.794 --> 42:52.706
l'm lookin' for Simon Lynch.
Do you know where he is?

42:52.754 --> 42:55.222
He suffered a minor head injury.
Nothing serious.

42:55.314 --> 42:58.624
We had to take him
down to X-ray.

42:58.674 --> 43:00.665
Where is the X-ray room?

43:00.754 --> 43:02.984
Radiology.
Seventh floor.

43:03.074 --> 43:05.110
Great. Thanks.

43:06.194 --> 43:08.424
No problem.

